latestIgtvVideos.title: Daily Shine Cleanup ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
During this pandemic, the most precious place for a woman :The Beauty Salons are unfortunately shut.
But what if you can get a cleanup at your Home ❤️🤪 Ingredients
2tsp Honey
1tsp Sugar
1/2tsp Olive oil

Mix the ingredients and store it in a container later use.

1.Clean your face with a facewash or cleanser 
2. Apply the mixture all over the face.
3. Massage and scrub the mixture for about 10-15 mins
4. Leave the pack for 10-15 mins more and rinse it with luke warm water.
5. You can apply this mixture everyday before going to sleep and wake up with a soft and shiny skin

The herbal pack is best for all skin types and ages, . From toddlers to aged people.
My girls and also my guy friends can try this at home.

Honey works as antioxidants,while sugar works as a natural scrub and olive oil works as moisturer.

PS- The one who has extreme oil and pimply skin with puss formation should not practice this.

I hope this information helps you to get a healthy soft skin❤️ Toodles.

latestIgtvVideos.title: 🍅Tomato Face Pack🍅
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This pack is generally for mature/aged  and pigmented skin. While works wonders for oil skin as well

Ingredients 
1tsp oats
1tsp jaggery /Gud/ Goad
1/2 tsp almond oil
1tsp tomato puree

Mix all the ingredients.

1.Clean the face with cleanser or facewash 
2. Apply the fresh pack 
3. The pack might burn a bit due to citric present in tomato.
4.Keep the pack for 10-15 mins and rinse it off with luke warm water.

This herbal face pack is excellent for oily  and aged skin.
Jaggery has oil control properties while almond oil balances the oil proportion, oats lightens up your complexion and lastly tomato reduces  scars or bacterial infection(if any).

latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY Spinach Face Pack.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sensitive skin is allergic to citrc and acidic packs, this pack works wonders for skin like me.

Ingredients:
1tsp Grinded Spinach
1tsp Sandalwood/Chandan powder
1tsp Honey.
Mix the ingredients well.

1.Clean the face with cleanser or facewash 
2. Apply milk over and under eye area,for soothing effect.
3. Apply the fresh pack 
4. Keep it for 10 minutes and rinse it off with lukewarm water.

Spinach is full of vitamins and minerals.This packs hydrates the skin and reduces the blemishes.
Apply the pack twice a week for effective results.
